  	<h2>Overview</h2>
  			
<p>Splunk has added several new IdPs for Single Sign-On (SSO) to their growing list of SAML providers. Please visit <a href="http://docs.splunk.com/Documentation/Splunk/6.5.0/Security/ConfigureSSOinSplunkWeb">documentation</a> for general SAML information. <br/>NOTE: you must be logged in to access the documentation pages.<br/>Select the product names below for details and configuration options.</p>

<p>In addition Splunk now supports <a href="http://docs.splunk.com/Documentation/Splunk/6.5.0/Security/ConfigureDuo">Duo Security</a> two-factor authentication</p>

